title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, ESPN's Laura Rutledge joins from London to preview her sit down interview with Russell Wilson. SI's Senior NBA Writer Chris Mannix calls in to discuss the potential of NBA prospect Victor Wembanyama. Plus, Hall of Fame QB Troy Aikman shares the the most unusual thing he ever gave out during Halloween.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
